# Database Migrations Directory

This directory contains database migration scripts for HushRyd backend.

## Creating a new migration

Create a new file with the naming convention: `YYYYMMDDHHMMSS_description.js`

Example: `20241209120000_add_user_indexes.js`

## Migration file structure

```javascript
module.exports = {
  async up(mongoose) {
    // Migration logic here
  },
  
  async down(mongoose) {
    // Rollback logic here
  }
};
```

## Running migrations

- `npm run migrate` - Run all pending migrations
- `npm run migrate:status` - Show migration status
- `npm run migrate:rollback` - Rollback last migration
